講冇用架<br />\n同出面講啦<br />\n做文宣啦"},{"pid":"d0a11caf04cd569a629cf46caf9a8dd5801843bb","tid":1689350,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"其實想問好耐<br />\n日日叫人罷工<br />\n咁手停口停既人點樣罷法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月月清又點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b4c15cb745f2588c760110242a435f05267ed6","tid":1689350,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:39:46.000Z","msg":"我只會跪手足，懇求大家唔好習慣同放棄。抄一個手足既說話<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「你若放棄，誰衛我城」</span></span>，希望大家可以做到可以失望但唔好絕望，堅持下去先可以見到奇蹟!雖然好多香港人都唔明呢句說話既含義，但我仍想講多次<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「光復香港 時代革命」</span></span>"},{"pid":"0dfebf7b6197a14ed2ef196d5386241090f474d4","tid":1689350,"uid":252007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0a11caf04cd569a629cf46caf9a8dd5801843bb","tid":1689350,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"其實想問好耐<br />\n日日叫人罷工<br />\n咁手停口停既人點樣罷法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月月清又點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"咁唔係個個都係咁啩？<br />\n仲有<br />\n前線嗰班買gear買到得返十幾蚊日日捱麵包<br />\n佢哋一樣出去擋子彈<br />\n有人辭埋工出去發夢<br />\n甚至有人犧牲埋性命<br />\n咁呢班人又點計？<br />\n佢哋有佢哋犧牲<br />\n其他人呢？"},{"pid":"55517c70c6434fa51b8992c2b79b77b03b2e97c9","tid":1689350,"uid":132986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"停幾日嘅成效一定大過weekend 抗爭<br />\n係港奴放低唔到包袱先會搞到咁多死傷<br />\n<br />\n停一星期就有經濟問題嘅人要檢討吓<br />\n利申freelance"},{"pid":"7f0a3e275254716fe4300abc28b53f73233f0562","tid":1689350,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:44:34.000Z","msg":"大三罷"},{"pid":"5ea9252e83b89c2d3263cd29c1f760a6ed5b65ac","tid":1689350,"uid":132986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82929be5ff67592fd07f4fe26c375ddf5b924efe","tid":1689350,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"連續罷幾日好快就會習慣罷工，但罷1日都好難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:45:39.000Z","msg":"8月5已經試過<br />\n但港奴係要被罷工，根本就係唔想作出任何犧牲，最唔暴力嘅方法都唔用，日日用把口嚟抗爭"}]}